law.text: The Justice and Public Safety Cabinet shall forward one (1) copy of each photograph, set of fingerprints, and general description report received by it in a criminal case to the Federal Bureau of Investigation.
law.history: Amended 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 77, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. V, sec. 24(1). -- Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 129, sec. 3, effective June 19, 1958.
